products.title: Addict Terrazzo Grey Roller Blind
products.description: The perfect blend of function and style, the addict terrazzo roller blind will help you make the most of your living space. This polyester fabric roller blind allows you to control the natural light levels in the room whilst providing a chic decorative touch. This artistic blend of cool greys is certainly eye-catching with a distinct urban vibe. Product id: sdb-rbx2004 fabric colour: terrazo grey material: 100% polyester headrail: durable aluminium roller tube supported by white steel brackets - top, face or side fix control type: smooth continuous-looped chain energy saving rating: er2 - medium energy saving value - effective thermal retention light filtering: yes addict terrazzo grey roller blind in grey/black.
